long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Easily connect your LinkedIn account to Seleqt.ai with our Chrome extension.

Seleqt.ai is an AI-powered recruitment platform designed to streamline your candidate search process. This extension simplifies the connection process, enabling users to easily integrate your LinkedIn account into our advanced sourcing, screening, and outreach tools.

With this extension, you can:

- Link your LinkedIn account to automate candidate outreach.
- Save time by letting Seleqt.ai handle repetitive tasks like sourcing and screening.
- Focus on meaningful conversations with the best-matched candidates.
